buildSVG(uint256).details: Builds the SVG image for a given token ID

returns._0: string The SVG image as a string

params.tokenId: The ID of the token to burn

constructor.details: Constructor to initialize the BaseColorPalettesNFT contract

params.baseColorsAddress: The address of the BaseColors contract
params.initialMaxSupply: The initial maximum supply of NFTs
params.initialMintPrice: The initial price for minting an NFT

currentSupply().details: Returns the current supply of tokens

getColorName(string).details: Function to get color name from hex. This function is used to get the color name from the base colors contract. If not found, it returns the hex color.

isUniqueCombination(string[]).details: Checks if a color combination is unique

params.colors: An array of color hex codes

returns._0: bool indicating if the combination is unique

isValidHexCode(string).details: Checks if a given string is a valid hex color code

returns._0: bool indicating if the string is a valid hex color code

mint(uint256[],address).details: Mints a new token with colors from provided BaseColors token IDs

params.tokenIds: Array of BaseColors token IDs to use for colors

mintBatch(uint256[][],address).details: Mints multiple tokens in a single transaction

params.batchTokenIds: Array of arrays containing BaseColors token IDs for each palette

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

tokenURI(uint256).details: Generates the token URI for a given token ID

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

withdraw().details: Withdraws the contract balance to the owner

pause().notice: Can only be called by the contract owner

toggleMinting().notice: Can only be called by the contract owner

unpause().notice: Can only be called by the contract owner

updateMaxSupply(uint256).notice: Can only be called by the contract owner

updateMintPrice(uint256).notice: Can only be called by the contract owner
